HmDomain
--------

:py:class:`hm.Domain` is a class to represent the spatiotemporal
model domain.

Creating a HmDomain
-------------------

The constructor function `hm.set_domain` takes the following
arguments:

- ``filename_or_obj``
- ``modeltime``
